tables.loadSelectStatement:
LOAD [Address] AS [Address],
	[City] AS [City],
	[ContactName] AS [ContactName],
	[Country] AS [Country],
	[Region] AS [Region],
	[Customer] AS [Customer],
	[CustomerID] AS [CustomerID],
	[Fax] AS [Fax],
	[Phone] AS [Phone],
	[PostalCode] AS [PostalCode],
	[CountryCode] AS [CountryCode],
	[Latitude] AS [Latitude],
	[Longitude] AS [Longitude]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Customers);

LOAD [EmployeeID] AS [EmployeeID],
	[Extension] AS [Extension],
	[EmployeeName] AS [EmployeeName],
	[EmployeeGender] AS [EmployeeGender],
	[Hire Date] AS [Hire Date],
	[Office] AS [Office],
	[Supervisor] AS [Supervisor],
	[JobTitle] AS [JobTitle],
	[AnnualSalary] AS [AnnualSalary],
	[SalesTarget] AS [SalesTarget]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Employees);

LOAD [Office] AS [Office],
	[OfficeLocation] AS [OfficeLocation]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Offices);

LOAD [OrderDate] AS [OrderDate],
	[CustomerID] AS [CustomerID],
	[EmployeeID] AS [EmployeeID],
	[ShippingCost] AS [ShippingCost],
	[OrderID] AS [OrderID],
	[ShippingCompany] AS [ShippingCompany],
	[DeliveryDate] AS [DeliveryDate]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is OrderHeader);

LOAD [CategoryID] AS [CategoryID],
	[CategoryName] AS [CategoryName],
	[Department] AS [Department],
	[Description] AS [Description]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Category);

LOAD [ProductID] AS [ProductID],
	[CategoryID] AS [CategoryID],
	[ProductName] AS [ProductName],
	[SupplierID] AS [SupplierID]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Products);

LOAD [OrderID] AS [OrderID],
	[ProductID] AS [ProductID],
	[Quantity] AS [Quantity],
	[Sales] AS [Sales],
	[Discount] AS [Discount],
	[CostOfSales] AS [CostOfSales],
	[GrossProfit] AS [GrossProfit]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is OrderDetails);

LOAD [SupplierID] AS [SupplierID],
	[Supplier] AS [Supplier],
	[SupplierContact] AS [SupplierContact],
	[SupplierCountry] AS [SupplierCountry]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Suppliers);

LOAD [EmployeeID] AS [EmployeeID],
	[TerritoryID] AS [TerritoryID]
FROM [lib://AttachedFiles/International Apparel Data.xlsx]
(ooxml, embedded labels, table is Territories);
